data.description: Elegant 3 bedroom 2 bath townhome in the exclusive community of The Enclave at Horseshoe Bay.  This upscale property is located near the amenity area which includes a large pool, covered gathering area with rest rooms, outdoor kitchen with large built-in grill, gazebo, and mail center.  The interior of the home includes wood floors throughout except in bathrooms, laundry, and kitchen, added recessed lighting in the bedrooms, under cabinet lights in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances including Bosch range and microwave oven, and Kitchen Aid dishwasher.  Relax on the large covered back patio with a view of the pool area.  The Enclave is situated in Horseshoe Bay West near Lake LBJ and world class Horseshoe Bay Resort with 4 championship golf courses, multiple restaurants, pools, marina, tennis, and pickle ball courts.  This townhome will make a perfect lock and leave primary residence or a vacation home.  Don't miss seeing this one.  It's a true gem!
